%%[doesWhat doclatex
Simplifies expressions based on their structure & annotation:
\begin{itemize}
\item Replace @fromInteger (...) :: Int@ with its @Int@ equivalent.
\item Replace @fromInteger (...) :: Integer@ with its @Integer@ equivalent.
\end{itemize}
